______________________________________________________________
______________________RECORDN ROUTES__________________________
______________________________________________________________
/create                 ----------      CREATE STUDENT RECORD
/record/:id             ----------      TO GET PARTICULAR RECORD
/record/edit/:id        ----------      TO EDIT PARTICULAR RECORD
/record/pdf/:id         ----------      TO DOWNLAOD PDF OF PARTICULAR RECORD
/record/certificate/:id ----------      TO DOWNLOAD CERTIFICATE OF PARTICULAR RECORD


